snippet.title: Super Rare Mixtape: Halloween Edition - Official Launch Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Super Rare Mixtape is a physical collection of 30+ indie horror games all on a single limited edition USB stick, available now. Check out the trailer for a peek at the games featured in this collection, including No Snake Hotel, Corpseocean, Bonnie's Bakery, Terminal, and more.
